Package: igraphlayout
Title: Manual Layout Editor for 'igraph' Objects
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mauricio",
           family = "Vargas Sepulveda",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "m.vargas.sepulveda@gmail.com")
Description: Manually edit the layout of 'igraph' objects using an interactive Shiny application.
    Provides a user-friendly interface to adjust node positions in graph visualizations and
    apply various layout algorithms from the 'igraph' package with a user-defined seed.
